steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"ffh0q","text":"Coat 6 well plates with Geltrex LDEV-Free Reduced Growth Factor Basement Membrane Matrix (Thermo Fisher Scientific), 1:100 dilution for 1 hour before cell passaging. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ecaad","text":"Old media is aspirated and replaced with 1ml of cell-culture PBS (Gibco, Thermo Fisher Scientific) ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"eod92","text":"PBS is aspirated and replaced with 0.5 mM EDTA (Thermo Fisher Scientific) made up in PBS. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"81il","text":"hiPSC are incubated in EDTA for   at   .","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":32,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":37,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"4gnp","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":300,"guid":"6838D630449311EDAB037B5C129D73F4","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}},"1":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"70754BD0449311EDAB037B5C129D73F4","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"37","unit":10}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"61jlh","text":"After 5 minutes, the EDTA is aspirated and cells are dissociated with media (E8 or mTesR 1). ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7mem2","text":"hiPSCs are then placed in new 6 well plates at the desired dilution.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4f34f","text":"All hiPSCs are fed daily with fresh media. All cells were maintained at 37°C and 5% carbon dioxide.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
